A. Important Rules (To Avoid
Problems)
Phones are good ONLY IF you follow these rules:
XX Don't Do This

o Don't sell retail prices

« Don't sell single units

¢ Don't compete with local phone shops
Do This Instead

«Focus on bulk / wholesale

¢ Use RFQ (Request for Quotation) only

e Show MOQ (Minimum Order Quantity)

o Target resellers and importers
